<text id="02-output-contract" title="Tailwind CSS — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying tailwind. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['tokens_in_config', 'cn_with_merge_used', 'no_hardcoded_token_equivalents', 'mobile_first_prefixes'],
  "properties": {
    "tokens_in_config": { "type": "boolean" },
    "cn_with_merge_used": { "type": "boolean" },
    "no_hardcoded_token_equivalents": { "type": "boolean" },
    "mobile_first_prefixes": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>tokens_in_config</item>
      <item>cn_with_merge_used</item>
      <item>no_hardcoded_token_equivalents</item>
      <item>mobile_first_prefixes</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tokens_in_config": true,
  "cn_with_merge_used": true,
  "no_hardcoded_token_equivalents": true,
  "mobile_first_prefixes": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tokens_in_config": false,
  "cn_with_merge_used": false,
  "no_hardcoded_token_equivalents": false,
  "mobile_first_prefixes": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-tokens-in-config).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
